<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Filming for Married At First Sight 2021 is currently under way in Sydney.</p>

<p>And Daily Mail Australia can exclusively reveal the identity of one of the grooms set to appear on Channel Nine's social experiment.</p>

